# Just need a distro?
</div>
<div class="right" markdown="1">
You can download *{project_name:}* from the [FUSE Forge Maven Repository](http://repo.fusesource.com/maven2) in the [{project_name:} area](http://repo.fusesource.com/maven2/org/fusesource/{project_id:}/).
